History
-------

0.9.0 (2020-01-23)
++++++++++++++++++

* Integration with Zotero
* Base search

0.5.0 (2019-02-05)
++++++++++++++++++

* Wagtail settings for footer text and analytics settings
* `kdl_wagtail_core` utils:
    * `paginate`
* `kdl_wagtail_core` template tags:
    * `get_page_children`
    * `get_analytics_id`


0.1.0 (2019-01-22)
++++++++++++++++++

* First release on PyPI.


